            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Inleiding",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<h4 id=\"stcpDiv\">3FM focust zich tijdens Serious Request 2013 in Leeuwarden op 800.000 kinderen die jaarlijks onnodig overlijden door diarree.</h4>\n<h4>Deze stille ramp is het gevolg van gebrek aan schoon drinkwater, zeep en toiletten.</h4>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": []
        },
        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "737995"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Informatie",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [],
            "sections": [
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "738007"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Feiten en cijfers",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"129.0480038459301\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\">Jaarlijks sterven 800.000 kinderen aan diarree.</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"129.0480038459301\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"114.15600340211392\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\">Dat zijn maar liefst 2.200 kinderen per dag,</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"25.008000745296478\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\">vergelijk dat met 70 volle schoolklassen per dag!</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"122.59200365352633\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\">Diarree is de oorzaak van bijna 11 % van allekindersterfte (&lt;5 jaar) wereldwijd.</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"274.47600818002223\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\">Het kindersterftecijfer (&lt;5 jaar) door diarree overstijgt hiermee het dodental van malaria, aids</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"129.55200386095046\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\">en mazelen bij elkaar.</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"74.05200220692157\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\">Slechte hygi\u00ebne, gebrek aan schoon drinkwater en gebrek aan toiletten is de oorzaak van</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"121.86000363171102\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\">88% van de sterfgevallen.</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"152.3880045415163\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\">Bij diarree krijgen slechts 4 op de 10 (39%) kinderen een behandeling.</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"22.74000067770481\" data-font-name=\"g_font_12_0\" dir=\"ltr\">Handen wassen met zeep na gebruik van het toilet of v\u00f3\u00f3r het eten verlaagt het aantal sterfgevallen met 48%</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"137.39648409473418\" data-font-name=\"g_font_5_0\" dir=\"ltr\">Kinderen in ontwikkelingslanden krijgen gemiddeld 3 x per jaar diarree.</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"3.6720001094341277\" data-font-name=\"g_font_7_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"28.287360843029028\" data-font-name=\"g_font_12_0\" dir=\"ltr\">1 op de 3 wereldburgers heeft geen toegang tot een hygi\u00ebnische wc</div>\n<div data-angle=\"0\" data-canvas-width=\"22.014720656089786\" data-font-name=\"g_font_12_0\" dir=\"ltr\"> </div>\n"
                        }
